%C A293680 .        /
%C A293680 . P(n-2)*
%C A293680 This sequence has building features in common with A293539.
%C A293680 The study of the first thousand dots shows an alternation of apparently chaotic phases and regular phases where a pattern repeats itself; unlike Langton's ant, this repetitive behavior doesn't last long. It is unknown if eventually a periodic pattern repeating itself infinitely emerges.
